Jim Ratcliffe wants to build a 'carbon neutral' mansion in the New Forest . 
  Ratcliffe is founder and chairman of chemical company Ineos . 
  He wants to demolish an existing beach house and replace it with the new mansion . 
  The house has a revolutionary jacking system which can lift itself up in the case of flooding . 
  The mansion will be virtually 'carbon-zero' and uses renewable energy . 
 